Class CommentList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.meditrackr.models.CommentList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CommentList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    CommentList: A list of comments. Allows adding and removing elements (by both index and comment), checking if a comment object exists in the array and retrieving the size of the list.
